            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Traditional Zoo CharmDiverse Animal Species: Encounter over 25 captivating animal species from around the world. Enjoy watching majestic creatures like lions, tigers, and elephants in their carefully designed habitats. Interact with friendly animals in the petting zoo section, perfect for younger visitors.Natural Habitats: Walk through lush, naturalistic enclosures that mimic the animals' native environments. Learn about the importance of conservation and animal welfare through educational displays and guided tours. Cutting-Edge AnimatronicsLifelike Animatronic Creatures: Marvel at the lifelike animatronic dinosaurs and other prehistoric creatures. Experience realistic movements and sounds that make these animatronic figures come to life.Interactive Exhibits: Engage with interactive displays that provide fascinating information about extinct species and their ecosystems.Participate in hands-on activities that are both fun and educational for all ages."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
